<parameternamelist>
<parametername direction="in">export_func</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>The pointer to the internal function which appends a single key-value pair to persisted settings. Don&apos;t store duplicated value. The name is subtree/key string, val is the string with value.</para>
